These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
2 different games are played: monopoly, poker
House: colonial, wooden
City: berlin, edinburgh
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, tiparillo
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, spanish
There 2 different types of food: banana, grapefruit
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person eating banana##1
2. the spanish is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the colonial house##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | sprite     | hot-chocolate |
| Game         | poker  | monopoly       |
| House           | wooden   | colonial    |
| City   | edinburgh     | berlin   |
| Cigar   | tiparillo      | game     |
| Nationality         | spanish | egyptian      |
| Food     | grapefruit       | banana           |

