.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, traveling
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, september
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, lily
2 different games are played: monopoly, billiard
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, chestnut
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, funk
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
6. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Beverage      | sprite         | cola       |
| Hobby          | camping        | traveling |
| Birthday           | september | november    |
| Flower   | lily        | marigold  |
| Game   | billiard        | monopoly       |
| Color           | chestnut            | amber        |
| Music-Genre     | funk            | pop       |

